<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="text-center bg-light p-5 rounded shadow">
        <h1 class="display-4 text-primary fw-bold">Welcome!</h1>
        <p class="lead mt-4">
            This is a modern <strong>online catalog application</strong> designed for educational institutions to efficiently manage courses, students, teachers, and grades in a transparent and user-friendly way.
